    "attributes": {
        "action": "Amend law to allow advertisement of cancer treatments in clinical trail stage",
        "additional_details": "We think this could lead to more people being aware of other treatments, and that as a result the NHS may have to update the treatments available.\r\n \r\nWe think that there are effective treatments available outside the NHS, and being phase 2 we believe there is evidence they work.\r\n",
        "background": "Amend existing legislation to allow the publication of advertisements for cancer treatments that have passed Phase 2 clinical trials. We believe this would give people more choice and more chance to find new treatments not available through the NHS.",
